## Which License Do I Need?

### ✓ Use PolyForm Noncommercial (FREE)

- Individual personal/family use
- Educational purposes and teaching
- Academic research and study
- Non-profit organizations (501(c)(3) or equivalent)
- Government institutions
- Hobby and personal projects
- Open-source projects (non-commercial)

**No registration required** - just include proper attribution!

### ✓ Use Commercial License (PAID)

- For-profit businesses and corporations
- Commercial products or SaaS applications
- Professional services to clients
- Internal business use at for-profit companies
- Revenue-generating applications
- Commercial redistribution or embedding

**Contact us:** weekend@weekendsuperhero.io

